@startuml
title UC-1 User-presented Mode Payment - Merchant Scans Customer QR
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam dpi 140
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam titleFontSize 15
skinparam legendFontSize 10
skinparam participantFontSize 11
skinparam actorFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowFontSize 10
skinparam ArrowColor #4A5568
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #5B6B82
skinparam ActorBorderColor #5B6B82

legend right
|= Color |= System |
|<#FFF2CC>| Consumer / Merchant |
|<#D4F1EA>| Your POS / Scanner |
|<#CFE2FF>| Your Backend / ACQP |
|<#FCE5CD>| Alipay+ client-side assist |
|<#F4CCCC>| Alipay+ backend |
|<#E1D5E7>| MPP Wallet / MPP Server |
----
|<#2F80ED>| Blue arrows = Alipay+ SDK / checkout calls |
|<#C0392B>| Red arrows = Alipay+ backend API calls |
|<#4A5568>| Gray arrows = non-Alipay API / SDK steps |
endlegend

actor Consumer #FFF2CC
actor "Store Cashier" as Cashier #FFF2CC
participant "Your POS / Scanner" as POS #D4F1EA
participant "Your Backend / ACQP" as ACQP #CFE2FF
participant "Alipay+ Backend" as AP #F4CCCC
participant "MPP Wallet App" as Wallet #E1D5E7
participant "MPP Server" as MPPServer #E1D5E7

autonumber "S00"

Consumer -> Wallet: Open wallet payment code page
Wallet -> MPPServer: Request payment code
MPPServer -> AP: getPaymentCode(...)
AP --> MPPServer: paymentCode / validity
MPPServer --> Wallet: Return payment code
Wallet --> Consumer: Display QR/bar code
Consumer -> Cashier: Present payment code
Cashier -> POS: Scan customer code and input amount
POS -> ACQP: Create in-store payment\n(codeValue, amount, merchant)
ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: pay(user-presented mode)
AP -> MPPServer: Route payment request\nwith decoded customer identity
alt Wallet requires confirmation
  MPPServer -> Wallet: Push payment confirmation
  Wallet -> Consumer: Show payment confirmation
  Consumer -> Wallet: Confirm / authenticate
end
Wallet --> MPPServer: Confirmation result
MPPServer --> AP: Payment result
AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: Sync payment result
AP -[#C0392B]> ACQP: notifyPayment(final status)
ACQP -[#C0392B]--> AP: SUCCESS ack
opt Callback missing or status still uncertain
  ACQP -[#C0392B]> AP: inquiryPayment(paymentRequestId or paymentId)
  AP -[#C0392B]--> ACQP: paymentResult S, F, or U
end
ACQP --> POS: Payment result
POS --> Cashier: Show success / fail / pending
Cashier --> Consumer: Complete sale

note over Wallet, MPPServer
The payment code is generated on the MPP side.
It is not generated by the merchant app or ACQP backend.
end note
@enduml
